name: inspiringbeans
overview: Inspiringbeans.com is an interactive education portal making college admission process simple and allows users to browse colleges on the basis of their preferred location and other attributes. Our ever growing database have more than 30.000 colleges and schools detailed information. Inspiringbeans Ranking Engine is among our major achievements which ranks colleges based on their placement, opening & closing rank, Social Activities such as fest, events, blogging, online discussions.
